{"tid":2400275,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"美國退出3年後　拜登政府將重返聯合國人權理事會","createTime":"2021-02-08T23:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T08:04:35.000Z","uid":204533,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4de3892b424ce0efbf07953c826875f660d361d5","tid":2400275,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:16:14.000Z","msg":"美國前總統川普以對以色列存在偏見以及缺乏改革為由，退出聯合國人權理事會3年之後，現任總統拜登（Joe Biden）政府將重新加入。<br />\n<br />\n國務院官員7日表示，國務卿布林肯（Antony Blinken）8日將宣布，美國將以觀察員身分重返總部設在日內瓦的人權理事會（United Nations Human Rights Council）。<br />\n<br />\n這位官員表示：「我們打算這樣做，因為知道改革理事會、讓理事會進步最有效的辦法，就是以合乎原則的方式與理事會往來。」<br />\n<br />\n這位官員說：「我們知道理事會有潛力成為對抗世界各地暴政與不公義的重要論壇，藉著參與會議，我們希望理事會改革，確定理事會實現那個潛能。」<br />\n<br />\n川普政府2018年以長期對以色列存有偏見且缺乏改革為由，退出人權理事會。（中央社）"},{"pid":"5bb36f36abd21c772c5aa5677476e43f44a70aeb","tid":2400275,"uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:17:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210208/2N6EOF43HFCDNGWQX2L46BDSG4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210208%2F2N6EOF43HFCDNGWQX2L46BDSG4%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=c3bcf70b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210208%2F2N6EOF43HFCDNGWQX2L46BDSG4%2F&h=452a5063\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210208/2N6EOF43HFCDNGWQX2L46BDSG4/</a>"},{"pid":"e3b4f2a01a1458468d953aa7ab01f83eba930e76","tid":2400275,"uid":129946,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:18:45.000Z","msg":"呢隻支那傀儡同柒婆一撚樣，真係為左鬥氣專登做同侵相反嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd43830d3dbf4932e84a49c26aff5bf59e6ea950","tid":2400275,"uid":204533,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:18:54.000Z","msg":"2020年10月13日，聯合國人權理事會（UNHRC）進行席次改選，投票結果出爐，<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">中國、俄羅斯、古巴、巴基斯坦、烏茲別克等人權狀況相當惡劣的國家高票當選</span></span></strong>。在亞太區，中國的得票雖然落後於巴基斯坦、烏茲別克和尼泊爾，卻仍獲得139票的高票。<br />\n......<br />\n蓬佩奧直指此次改選是「擁抱獨裁者」，他指出：「中國和俄羅斯、古巴都贏得聯合國人權理事會席位，這是暴君的勝利，聯合國的難堪。這是一個例證，一個指標，說明為什麼我們離開這個機構是正確的。當機構變得無可救藥，川普（Donald Trump）總統領導下的美國絕不會參與。」<br />\n<br />\n退出絕不是美國最後的殺手鐧，美國正在計畫拋開聯合國人權理事會、世界衛生組織、聯合國教科文組織乃至聯合國本身，建立一個新的「民主國家聯盟」，以處理新形態之下的國際事務。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/144717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F144717&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=fb603c71\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/144717</a>"},{"pid":"6e77e1dacbb537dc5ed71c5cdf9916f422f4a63a","tid":2400275,"uid":183758,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FKvopfO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFKvopfO.gif&h=fe854cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">民主黨垃撚圾</span>"},{"pid":"58cbaaf71af01d94dda366591bb58a8e1f4bc48a","tid":2400275,"uid":70771,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:18:58.000Z","msg":"姐係將口頭譴責作為跟住幾年既核心黎維護人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/throw.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509b444c745a75787720eea72e3f71b5e15f8d59","tid":2400275,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T23:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2775000/2776330/1014006_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2775000%2F2776330%2F1014006_1024.png&h=b7fd0581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/rights-10142020062416.html/china-rights.jpg/@@images/image\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fcantonese%2Fnews%2Frights-